INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Creativity','Theatre','In this workshop we will approach different ways of playing and making theatre. Every day we will prepare a little performance with fun and creativity for the next day’s plenary session. That means, we will create real performances and prepare everything we need ourselves: Storyline, acting, props, costumes, etc. If you like to play theatre or try it out, join in! No acting experience required. No one will be pressured to participate in the performance ;-). ',0,1);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Creativity','Theatre','Leader: Maria Winter<br>Location: tent in village 8<br>Participants: 15<br>Please bring:<br>Days: Tue, Wen, Fri, Sat',0,2);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Creativity','Rastas – Self-Made of Artificial Hair','We will turn back time to the nineties and celebrate the comeback of “Rastas”. Stars like Beyoncé or the girls of Tic Tac Toe were wearing “Rastas“ and we will revive this look today. In this workshop I will show you how to plait artificial hair into your hair. All you have to bring along is a lot of fun and a little patience. Making a new hairstyle can last for hours. For this reason in the workshop we will just learn and try a lot of things, so you can do the hairstyle in summer with your friends. If you want to you can bring something to sit on and a friend with whom you want to work together. ',0,1);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Creativity','Rastas – Self-Made of Artificial Hair','Leader: Lisa Opel<br>Location: WS tent 1<br>Participants: 15<br>Please bring: something to sit on <br>Days: Wen',0,2);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Creativity','Games that Need No material','Do you like playing games spontaneously? Do you like games without any preparation work which you can play nearly everywhere? Maybe you are planning some games with your YMCA-group? Or you know the feeling when you missed the bus and have to wait for half an hour with 30 kids jumping around and you’re desperate for something to do to kill time? Or you just enjoy playing games with your friends and having fun? In this workshop you can share your experiences with games that need neither material nor preparation und get active yourself. If you have ideas of your own, please share them in this workshop. We will quickly be ready to play! ',0,1);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Creativity','Games that Need No material','Leader: Carolin Münch<br>Location: Pavilon 3<br>Participants: 18<br>Please bring: sport shoes<br>Days: Wen',0,2);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Creativity','Develop Your Own Game!','Leader: Carolin Münch<br>Location: Pavilon 3<br>Participants: 18<br>Please bring: sport shoes<br>Days: Sat',0,3);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Creativity','Develop Your Own Game!','You like playing games together with nice people in a group? There are lots of possibilities to play: with your friends, in your YMCA-group, at camps, at school, in sports, in the water or on the land. Certainly you know lots of games which are real fun. In this workshop you will discover something new! Together with the others you can invent new ideas for group games and develop your own games. You will learn what is needed and what should be considered so that a game can be realized and everybody has fun! Of course, every game will be tested!',0,2);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Creativity','Henna Tattoo','Di10, Mi10, Fr10, Sa10',0,0);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Creativity','Henna Tattoo','Do you want a tattoo for few days? Try Henna tattoo! It''s a botanical color for the skin. You can draw on your skin whatever you like, but the original patterns come from India. If you have a sensitive skin you better take care and try it out beforehand. The pen is like a tube. You''re drawing directly on your skin. But before you try, I''ll show you how to use it. Let it dry for about one hour, then rub off the dry color and your Henna Tattoo is finished! If you''re interested, you''re welcome to my workshop!',0,1);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Creativity','Henna Tattoo','Leader: Madlen Wenzel<br>Location: Pavilion 8<br>Participants: 10<br>Please bring: -<br>Days: Tue, Wen, Fri, Sat',0,2);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Sport and activity','Jugger','Di05, Mi05, Fr05, Sa05',0,0);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Sport and activity','Jugger','Jugger is a sport inspired by the 1989 film The Salute of the Jugger.<br>We will play this game with two teams. Each team must appoint one running man who has to catch the “jugger” (ball) and put the jugger into the goal of the other team. Your own team members’ task is to protect their running man with some kind of a stick. You have to run a lot in this game but I can promise you, you will have a lot of fun',0,1);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Sport and activity','Jugger','Leader: Anne Bott<br>Location: Soccer pitch<br>Participants: 12<br>Please wear sports clothes.<br>Days: Tue, Wen, Fri, Sat',0,2);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Sport and activity','Indiaca','Di14, Fr14',0,0);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Sport and activity','Indiaca','Indiaca is a typical YMCA-game played by the rules of volleyball. Instead of a ball you throw the Indiaca over the net. If it hits the ground in your own part of the field the other team scores a point. Try it out!',0,1);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Sport and activity','Indiaca','Leader: Julia Winkel<br>Location: Volleyball court<br>Participants: 12<br>Please bring: -<br>Days: Tue, Fri',0,2);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Sport and activity','Ultimate','Di13',0,0);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Sport and activity','Ultimate','Ultimate Frisbee is a competitive team sport played with a frisbee. The spirit of the game is decisive for Ultimate. Most important are the principles of fair play and having fun.',0,1);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Sport and activity','Ultimate','Leader: Christian Elges<br>Location: playing field 1<br>Participants: 12<br>Please bring: sportswear<br>Days: Tue',0,2);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Sport and activity','Unihockey','Mi13',0,0);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Sport and activity','Unihockey','Some simple rules, teams with 4-5 players on each field, two little goals… and 90 minutes later you will know what you’ve done! Hockey for Newcomer.',0,1);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Sport and activity','Unihockey','Leader: Christian Elges<br>Location: playing field 1<br>Participants: 12<br>Please bring: sportswear<br>Days: Wen',0,2);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Sport and activity','Intercrosse','Fr13',0,0);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Sport and activity','Intercrosse','INTERCROSSE is a fast team sport with simple rules. You will get in contact with eachother, for your team will only be abe to winn if you understand eachother. It’s a fair game: you are neither allowed to touch the others with your body nor with your racket.',0,1);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Sport and activity','Intercrosse','Leader: Christian Elges<br>Location: playing field 1<br>Participants: 12<br>Please bring: sportswear<br>Days: Fri',0,2);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Sport and activity','Flag Football','Sa13',0,0);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Sport and activity','Flag Football','Do you know American Football? Then you will be surprised. There will be no violence – you can stop the other one just by stealing his band. So not only the ball is important for you.',0,1);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Sport and activity','Flag Football','Leader: Christian Elges<br>Location: playing field 1<br>Participants: 12<br>Please bring: sportswear<br>Days: Sat',0,2);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Sport and activity','Low Ropes Course  – Team Challenge','Mi14, Fr15, Sa15',0,0);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Sport and activity','Low Ropes Course  – Team Challenge','Movable courses with ropes have become quite a popular tool in Outdoor Education where you learn by practical experience and adventure. The stations of the course can be used in a flexible way and motivate the participants to making exciting experiences. You can go through a low ropes course alone or in a team. And at every crossing point new challenges are waiting for you – for instance the “Lianengang”, the “Rettungsinsel”, or the “Sanduhr”. You don’t know these terms? Well, then come to this Workshop and find out about it!',0,1);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Sport and activity','Low Ropes Course  – Team Challenge','Leader: Diego Alberto Coloma Martinez<br>Location: Pavilon 1 / wood<br>Participants: 8 - 15<br>Please bring: -<br>Days: Wen, Fri, Sat',0,2);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Sport and activity','Discover Biblical Stories By Doing Sports','Fr08',0,0);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Sport and activity','Discover Biblical Stories By Doing Sports','To get in touch with Biblical texts and understand them you don´t always have to sit down and read a lot! You can also choose an athletic way to discover new things. In this workshop we will get the possibility to learn more about the Biblical message through different sport activities and make own experiences. We will get to know athletic people in Biblical times and find out, what God, the inventor of all movement and fitness, wants to tell us.',0,1);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Sport and activity','Discover Biblical Stories By Doing Sports','Leader: Carolin Münch<br>Location: event tent<br>Participants: max. 18<br>Please bring: your Bible, sport shoes and sports wear<br>Days: Tue',0,2);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Topics of Interest','George Williams – The Founder of the YMCA','Mi03',0,0);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Topics of Interest','George Williams – The Founder of the YMCA','When was the foundation of the YMCA? Who did that? And how did everything come to happen?<br>If you don’t know the answers to these questions or you want to know more about it, come to this workshop! We will go back to the roots of the YMCA and find answers to your questions.',0,1);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Topics of Interest','George Williams – The Founder of the YMCA','Leader: Julia Winkel<br>Location: tent in village 9<br>Participants: 20<br>Please bring: - <br>Days: Wen',0,2);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Topics of Interest','Israel and the Jews','Fr03',0,0);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Topics of Interest','Israel and the Jews','Israel – the Promised Land of the Old Testament and still one of the most controversial trouble spots in the world. So what does that mean for us? Information and discussion about the significance of Israel in today’s world.',0,1);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Topics of Interest','Israel and the Jews','Leader: Michael Götz<br>Location: tent in village 9<br>Participants: 20<br>Please bring: -<br>Days: Fri',0,2);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Topics of Interest','Israel and the Jews','Di11, Mi11, Fr11, Sa11',0,3);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Topics of Interest','I Don’t Want to Live On a Destroyed Planet!','Sustainable consumption and production – how can we as youth produce and consume in a sustainable way? What can we do and where do we need help? A Nigerian-German YMCA group is ready to discuss solutions and help us discover new paths to go ... – this is our planet! ',0,0);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Topics of Interest','I Don’t Want to Live On a Destroyed Planet!','Leader: Stefan Hoffmann<br>Location: Pavilion 9<br>Participants: max. 25<br>Please bring: -<br>Days: Tue, Wen, Fri, Sat',0,1);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Topics of Interest','Iran – Culture and Christianity','Sa09',0,0);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Topics of Interest','Iran – Culture and Christianity','After the Islamic Revolution Iran was totally changed. Entry? Nearly impossible. Freedom? A foreign word. Christians? Persecuted, tortured and killed. Thousands of young people have to escape from Iran. Public uncensored reports about the life and the people in Iran are rare. Darya is working in the Persian Church „Light“, which belongs to her parents. She stays in contact with people from underground churches and their pastors. In this workshop she wants to dissolve prejudices and give you an insight into the life of Christians in Iran.',0,1);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Topics of Interest','Iran – Culture and Christianity','Leader: Darya Baniamerian<br>Location: Pavilon 7<br>Participants: 15<br>Please bring: -<br>Days: Sat',0,2);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Topics of Interest','The Walk with Jesus','Fr07',0,0);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Topics of Interest','The Walk with Jesus','The Walk with Jesus is an active game and experience which is suitable for young people.',0,1);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Topics of Interest','The Walk with Jesus','Leader: Günter Lücking<br>Location: Pavilion 2<br>Participants: 25<br>Please bring: - <br>Days: Fri',0,2);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Topics of Interest','The besieged city','Di07',0,0);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Topics of Interest','The besieged city','A role-play - the medieval town „Trotzburg“ is under siege from the „Hochbergern“.  They blame ther „Trotzenberger“ for having killed a businessman. And they demand the killer’s extradition within one hour. How may this conflict be solved? What will the persons do who are involved? Will you find a solution?',0,1);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Topics of Interest','The besieged city','Leader: Günter Lücking<br>Location: Pavilion 2<br>Participants: 12<br>Please bring: -<br>Days: Tue',0,2);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Topics of Interest','The Key-Game','The key-game  - a role-play that covers the topic of reconciliation. Often we try to blame others. Is there the option of reconsiliation? How can this be possible? What is important in cases of conflict? How does a salutary way of reconciliation look like? ',0,0);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Topics of Interest','The Key-Game','eader: Günter Lücking<br>Location: Pavilion 2 <br>Participants: 12<br>Please bring: -<br>Days: Wen',0,1);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Topics of Interest','Courage and strength for your daily life','Sa03',0,0);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Topics of Interest','Courage and strength for your daily life','What gives you strength in your daily life? Where does you strength come from? How do you deal with challenges? Reading the bible and hearing an honest report we will see how we can go through our daily life with God on our side.',0,1);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Topics of Interest','Courage and strength for your daily life','Leader: Uwe Berger<br>Location: tent in village 9<br>Participants: max. 12<br>Please bring: -<br>Days: Sat',0,2);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Topics of Interest','Worship, praise and praying','Di06, Mi06, Fr06, Sa06',0,0);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Topics of Interest','Worship, praise and praying','Worship, praise and praying - How do you do it?<br>Bring your worship songs, prayers and thoughts and share them with others. When sometimes in our life time is short and we hustle from one appointment to the next is there time for a relationship between God and us?<br>With an emphasis on the Lord´s Prayer we will take a look at different ways to worship and communicate with God, the challenges we are facing, ways to overcome some of them and in general how we can have a healthy relationship with God in our normal day to day life.',0,1);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Topics of Interest','Worship, praise and praying','Leader: Nadine Jording<br>Location: Media Church<br>Participants: 10<br>Please bring: - <br>Days: Tue, Wen, Fri, Sat',0,2);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Topics of Interest','Christian values,society,politics and Europe.','What does the Scripture teaches us about ordering human society? <br>This workshop is about the relevance of the Bible for our daily social and political life.We discuss the meaning of  values  such as justice, solidarity,  sustainability, freedom and responsibility. This workshop is about  questions like<br>** What are your dreams for a Just Society?<br>** What are your main Christian values; which  social or political values are for you most important?<br>** What kind of society do you want to achieve?<br>** Which national and or international  political topics/issues do bother you?',0,0);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Topics of Interest','Christian values,society,politics and Europe.','Leader: Cees Brenner<br>Location: Pavilion 7<br>Participants: 15<br>Please bring: - <br>Days: Wen',0,1);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Trips','1. Serve the City (13:30 -17:30) ','A youth center close to Wittenberg needs our help! We will be painting and decorating and meeting nice people from the Youth Club. You don’t need any skills, just be ready to work and serve this community! We provide all technical expertise and equipment – you just add your willingness to help and your good mood! <br>Please don’t forget to wear clothes that may get dirty.<br>We will meet at the entrance of the Camp.',0,0);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Trips','2. Trip to the Lake (14:00 – 17:30 )','(only if the weather is good!)<br>We will go to a lake and enjoy the afternoon!<br>Don’t forget to bring swimwear and something to drink ;-)<br>We will meet at the bus.',0,0);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Others','Talkshops','Time: 15:00 – 16:00, Tent in village 9',1,0);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Others','Talkshops','Do you have questions about our morning session? Is there something that’s still on your mind? No problem! If you want to you can come to our „Talkshop“.  From three to four o’clock pm the speakers of the “morning sessions” will be waiting for you at the tent in village no. 9. We will have time for you to answer your questions, to discuss things or just to listen to what is concerning you. We are looking forward to seeing you!',0,1);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Others','Preparing the Service','Wednesday: Time: 14:30 – 16:00',1,0);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Others','Preparing the Service','Today we’re having a special offer for you:<br>Tomorrow there will be our great trip to Berlin. We will end that day with a service in the Church on the “Alexanderplatz”. In this workshop we will prepare the service together. If you want to help us prepare and arrange the service you can join us and contribute your ideas.<br>Leader: Christine Becker<br>Location: tent of village 8',0,1);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Others','German for Beginners','Fr09',0,0);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Others','German for Beginners','You are not able to talk to the people of Wittenberg because you don’t speak German? This workshop might help you. We will learn some basic sentences and expressions in German. Hopefully, by the end of this workshop you will be able to introduce yourself, to buy things in a German store and quite a few other things.',0,1);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Others','German for Beginners','Leader: Christine Becker<br>Location: Workshop-Tent 2<br>Participants: 10<br>Please bring: -<br>Days: Fri',0,2);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Others','Flashmob – Dance','Di12',0,0);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Others','Flashmob – Dance','Music, action, fun? Let´s dance! We will practice a dance choreography which will motivate us and others and bring them in motion! The additional idea is to teach our whole camp group the dance and in the end get a big dance flashmob started in the center of Berlin. If you have danceable music and suitable dance steps, please bring it to the workshop. Maybe we can choose one of your songs and choreography. You are a dancing expert? Or you don´t have any dancing experience and you think that you have two left feet? You don´t know if dancing is your thing? No problem at all! You can join this workshop in any case and get the moves!',0,1);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Others','Flashmob – Dance','Leader: Carolin Münch<br>Location: Plenary Tent <br>Participants: no limitation<br>Please bring: sport shoes<br>Days: Tue',0,2);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Others','My car- the unknown being','Mi17',0,0);
INSERT INTO `Kategorie_Tab_Text` VALUES (3,'Workshops','Others','My car- the unknown being','A basic course for all who want to get to know their car better. How do I change tires? How can I check the oil level? What do I need to know as a driver in Germany?',0,1);
